nodes.text: Major Alinn Varth was a female officer in Rogue Squadron. In 25 ABY she held the position of Rogue Nine, and along with Major Inyri Forge, was one of the sub-commanders of the squadron to Colonel Gavin Darklighter. She fought at the Battle of Dantooine, Battle of Ithor, Battle of Kalarba, and Second Battle of Sernpidal.
